<view class="container data-v-5de8346d"><text class="page-title data-v-5de8346d">申请成为店长</text><text class="page-desc data-v-5de8346d">填写以下信息，提交入驻申请后等待平台审核。</text><view class="section data-v-5de8346d"><text class="section-label data-v-5de8346d">门店信息</text><view class="form-group data-v-5de8346d"><text class="form-label data-v-5de8346d">门店名称 *</text><input class="form-input data-v-5de8346d" placeholder="如：XX造型" value="{{a}}" bindinput="{{b}}"/></view><view class="form-group data-v-5de8346d"><text class="form-label data-v-5de8346d">联系电话 *</text><input class="form-input data-v-5de8346d" type="number" placeholder="门店联系电话" value="{{c}}" bindinput="{{d}}"/></view><view class="form-group data-v-5de8346d"><text class="form-label data-v-5de8346d">门店地址</text><input class="form-input data-v-5de8346d" placeholder="门店详细地址（选填）" value="{{e}}" bindinput="{{f}}"/></view><view class="form-group data-v-5de8346d"><text class="form-label data-v-5de8346d">门店简介</text><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="form-textarea data-v-5de8346d" placeholder="简单介绍门店（选填）" maxlength="200" value="{{g}}" bindinput="{{h}}"/></block></view></view><view class="section data-v-5de8346d"><text class="section-label data-v-5de8346d">营业时间</text><view class="hours-row data-v-5de8346d"><picker class="data-v-5de8346d" mode="time" value="{{j}}" bindchange="{{k}}"><view class="time-picker data-v-5de8346d">{{i}}</view></picker><text class="time-sep data-v-5de8346d">至</text><picker class="data-v-5de8346d" mode="time" value="{{m}}" bindchange="{{n}}"><view class="time-picker data-v-5de8346d">{{l}}</view></picker></view></view><view class="section data-v-5de8346d"><text class="section-label data-v-5de8346d">申请人信息</text><view class="info-row data-v-5de8346d"><text class="info-label data-v-5de8346d">微信昵称</text><text class="info-value data-v-5de8346d">{{o}}</text></view><view class="info-row data-v-5de8346d"><text class="info-label data-v-5de8346d">手机号</text><text class="info-value data-v-5de8346d">{{p}}</text></view></view><view class="bottom-area data-v-5de8346d"><button class="btn-submit data-v-5de8346d" bindtap="{{q}}">提交申请</button><text class="submit-hint data-v-5de8346d">提交后将在1-3个工作日内完成审核</text></view></view>